; @dynamic-labs-sdk/react-hooks has not kept up with @dynamic-labs-sdk/client.
; The highest published react-hooks is 1.8.2 (peer-pinned to client@1.8.0 exact),
; while client/evm are on 1.14.x. There is no react-hooks version that satisfies
; client@1.14.x today, so we install with peer-dep resolution relaxed. The lockfile
; still pins exact versions, and `npm audit` still works.
;
; If/when Dynamic publishes react-hooks@1.14.x (or the dashboard migrates off
; react-hooks), delete this file.
legacy-peer-deps=true
